## Documentation Standards

### Code Documentation
- Write comprehensive docstrings for all functions
- Document complex business logic inline
- Maintain up-to-date API documentation
- Document configuration options and environment variables
- Keep README files current with project changes

### Architecture Documentation
- Document system architecture and design decisions
- Maintain database schema documentation
- Document API contracts and integration points
- Keep deployment and operations documentation current
- Document security considerations and compliance

